Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with autonomously driving vehicles and perception of the local environment, which are common topics in robotics research.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper discusses object detection and tracking, which are common topics in computer vision.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper uses a Labeled Multi-Bernoulli filter, which is a machine learning algorithm commonly used in object tracking.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely for the same reason as cs.AI.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with controlling autonomous vehicles based on perception of the environment.
